001 Sign up
Preconditions:
- you are at the home page (https://qa-complexapp.onrender.com/)

1. In the Username input field enter valid username (yuliiaborodynska)
2. In the Email input field enter valid email (yuliia@mail.com)
3. In the Password input field enter valid pasword (123Qwertyasd)
4. Click Sign up for OurApp button

ER: You are redirected to your account page at the OurApp


